column5: I don't know any psychiatrist or support group but you can try searching on Facebook or just ask your question there since every Algerian has a fb account so you'll probably get more answers. And if you want to talk i'm here, just dm me. Also i'm so sorry for what happened to you, hope you'll feel better soon.

You still have yourself to live for, even if you're alone. I'm in the same boat as you, i have no motivation at all, i'm stuck in this infernal circle, too afraid to do anything because i know i'll fail.
Why are you doing all this to yourself?
